In designing public cloud, he has an understanding of the services however real time administration / management of services was an opportunity for improvement.   Overall, would recommend for second review prior sending it to the client.', 'submitted', '2025-09-07 20:42:55.022877+00', '2025-09-07 20:42:55.654149+00');


